Free Home Control System
Author: ufonCZK@gmail.com

Purpose
Free home automation system mainly for controlling solar panels, pumps, valves and gas heaters with OpenTherm protocol

Platform
ARM Cortex-M3 based MCU, tested with TI Stellaris LM3S6395

Features
Ethernet interface with WEb server
OLED 128x64 Display, Rotary encoder user interface
microSD card storeage with 4GB available
modular power interfaces (optotriacs, relays, temp-sensors etc)

Status
Under developemnt

Release
v0.0.1 Working concept
